#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter provides an overview of the core features and the typical "
"workflows. The most important parts are <xref linkend=\"introduction-nutshell"
"\"/> and <xref linkend=\"scripting\"/>, which together should allow every "
"new user to directly start using &rocs;."
msgstr ""
"To poglavje nudi pregled osnovnih funkcij in tipičnih delovnih tokov. "
"Najpomembnejša dela sta <xref linkend=\"introduction-nutshell\"/> in <xref "
"linkend=\"scripting\"/>, ki naj bi skupaj omogočila vsakemu novemu "
"uporabniku, da neposredno začne uporabljati &rocs;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "Goals, Target Audience, and Workflows"
msgstr "Cilji, ciljno občinstvo in delovni tokovi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; is a Graph Theory Tool for everybody interested in designing and "
"studying graph algorithms. In particular, those are"
msgstr ""
"&rocs; je orodje za teorijo grafov za vse, ki jih zanima načrtovanje in "
"preučevanje algoritmov grafov. Zlasti to so"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "lecturers, who want to demonstrate algorithms to their students,"
msgstr "predavatelji, ki želijo svojim študentom demonstrirati algoritme,"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"students and researchers, who want to see how their algorithm perform, and"
msgstr ""
"študente in raziskovalce, ki želijo videti, kako deluje njihov algoritem, in"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "everybody who is interested in data structures and algorithms."
msgstr "vsi, ki jih zanimajo podatkovne strukture in algoritmi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For all them, &rocs; provides an easy to use graphical editor for creating "
"graphs, a powerful scripting engine to execute algorithms, and several "
"helper tools for simulations, experiments, and graph exports. The typical "
"way of using &rocs; is to create a graph, either by hand (&ie;, dragging "
"nodes and edges to the whiteboard), or by using one of the graph generators. "
"Graph algorithms then can be implemented and executed on the created graph "
"and all changes, which the algorithm performs, are visible immediately in "
"the graph editor."
msgstr ""
"Za vse &rocs; ponuja enostaven grafični urejevalnik za ustvarjanje grafov, "
"zmogljiv skriptni mehanizem za izvajanje algoritmov in več pomožnih orodij "
"za simulacije, poskuse in izvoze grafov. Tipičen način uporabe &rocs; je "
"ustvarjanje grafa bodisi ročno (&ie; vlečenje vozlišč in robov na tablo) "
"bodisi z uporabo enega od generatorjev grafov. Algoritme na grafih lahko "
"nato implementiramo in izvajamo na ustvarjenem grafu in vse spremembe, ki "
"jih algoritem izvede, so takoj vidne v urejevalniku grafov."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A Screenshot of &rocs;.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &rocs;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A Screenshot of &rocs;.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &rocs;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "&rocs; in a Nutshell"
msgstr "&rocs; zelo na kratko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every &rocs; session is a project: when opening &rocs; an empty project is "
"created, when loading some project it becomes the current project. Hereby, a "
"project itself consists of <emphasis>graph documents</emphasis>, "
"<emphasis>scripts/algorithms</emphasis>, and a <emphasis>journal</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka seja &rocs; je projekt: ko odprete &rocs; se ustvari prazen projekt, "
"ko naložimo kakšen projekt postane trenutni projekt. Pri tem je sam projekt "
"sestavljen iz <emphasis>grafičnih dokumentov</emphasis>, <emphasis>skriptov/"
"algoritmov</emphasis> in <emphasis>dnevnika</emphasis>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graph Documents"
msgstr "Dokumenti grafov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A graph document represents the content of a whiteboard in the graph editor. "
"It contains information about the user defined node and edge types, their "
"properties, and about the already created nodes and edges. This is, &rocs; "
"understands the set of all nodes and edges of a graph document to form a "
"(not necessarily connected) graph. Everything belonging to a graph document "
"is accessible by the script engine via the global object "
"<userinput><command>Document</command></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Dokument z grafom predstavlja vsebino table v urejevalniku grafov. Vsebuje "
"informacije o uporabniško definiranih vrstah vozlišč in robov, njihovih "
"lastnostih ter o že ustvarjenih vozliščih in robovih. To je &rocs; razume "
"nabor vseh vozlišč in robov dokumenta grafa, da tvori (ne nujno povezan) "
"graf. Vse, kar pripada grafičnemu dokumentu, je dostopno skriptnemu "
"mehanizmu prek globalnega objekta <userinput><command>Dokument</command></"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edge Types"
msgstr "Vrste robov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In some scenarios, graphs consist of different types of edges (&eg;, an "
"undirected graph plus the tree edges computed by a breadh-first-search "
"algorithm) that shall be handled and displayed differently. For this, "
"besides a default edge type, you can define arbitrary other edge types. Each "
"edge type has its individual visual representation, dynamic properties, and "
"can be set to be either undirected or directed. The scripting interface "
"provides convenience methods to specifically access only edges of specific "
"types."
msgstr ""
"V nekaterih scenarijih so grafi sestavljeni iz različnih vrst robov (&eg; "
"neusmerjeni graf in drevesni robovi, izračunani z algoritmom iskanja najprej "
"v širino), ki bodo obravnavani in prikazani drugače. Za to lahko poleg "
"privzete vrste robov določite poljubne druge vrste robov. Vsaka vrsta robov "
"ima svojo individualno vizualno predstavitev, dinamične lastnosti in jih je "
"mogoče nastaviti kot neusmerjene ali usmerjene. Vmesnik za skripte ponuja "
"priročne metode za poseben dostop samo do robov določenih tipov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Node Types"
msgstr "Vrste vozlišč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Analog to edge types, you can define different types of nodes of a graph "
"(&eg;, to give some nodes special roles). Each node type has its own visual "
"representation and dynamic properties."
msgstr ""
"Analogno vrstam robov lahko definirate različne vrste vozlišč grafa (&eg; da "
"nekaterim vozliščem dodelite posebne vloge). Vsak tip vozlišča ima svojo "
"vizualno predstavitev in dinamične lastnosti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every (node or edge) element can have properties. Those properties must be "
"setup at the corresponding node or edge type. Properties are identified and "
"accessed by their names and can contain any value. To create new or change "
"existing properties, use the <guilabel>Element Types</guilabel> sidebar and "
"use the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Properties</guibutton> button to open the "
"property dialog."
msgstr ""
"Vsak element (vozlišče ali rob) ima lahko lastnosti. Te lastnosti morajo "
"biti nastavljene na ustrezno vrsto vozlišča ali roba. Lastnosti so "
"identificirane in dostopne po njihovih imenih in lahko vsebujejo poljubno "
"vrednost. Če želite ustvariti nove ali spremeniti obstoječe lastnosti, "
"uporabite stransko vrstico <guilabel>Vrste elementov</guilabel> in "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-properties.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject ></inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Lastnosti</"
"guibutton> gumb za odpiranje pogovornega okna lastnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the scripting engine to access registered properties and "
"change their values. In the following example we assume that the property "
"<quote>weight</quote> is registered for the default edge type."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do registriranih lastnosti in spreminjanje njihovih vrednosti "
"lahko uporabite tudi skriptni mehanizem. V naslednjem primeru "
"predpostavljamo, da je lastnost <quote>weight</quote> registrirana za "
"privzeti tip roba."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"var nodes = Document.nodes()\n"
"for (var i = 0; i &lt; nodes.length; ++i){\n"
"    nodes[i].weight = i;\n"
"}\n"
"for (var i = 0; i &lt; nodes.length; ++i){\n"
"    Console.log(\"weight of node \" + i + \": \" + nodes[i].weight);\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"var nodes = Document.nodes()\n"
"for (var i = 0; i &lt; nodes.length; ++i){\n"
"    nodes[i].weight = i;\n"
"}\n"
"for (var i = 0; i &lt; nodes.length; ++i){\n"
"    Console.log(\"teža vozla \" + i + \": \" + nodes[i].weight);\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tutorial"
msgstr "Vadnica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this section we want to create an example project to explore some of the "
"most important functions of &rocs;. The goal is to create a graph and a "
"script that illustrates a simple 2-approximate algorithm for the "
"<emphasis>minimum vertex cover</emphasis> problem. The minimum vertex cover "
"problem is the problem to find a subset of graph nodes C of minimal size "
"such that each graph edge is connected to at least one node in C. This "
"problem is known to be NP-hard and we want to illustrate how to find an "
"approximation of factor 2 by computing a matching in the given graph."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku želimo ustvariti primer projekta za raziskovanje nekaterih "
"najpomembnejših funkcij &rocs;. Cilj je ustvariti graf in skript, ki "
"ponazarja preprost 2-približni algoritem za problem <emphasis>najmanjšega "
"pokritja vozlišč</emphasis>. Problem minimalnega pokrivanja vozlišč je "
"problem najti podmnožico vozlišč grafa C minimalne velikosti, tako da je "
"vsak rob grafa povezan z vsaj enim vozliščem v C. Znano je, da je ta problem "
"NP-težek in želimo ponazoriti, kako poiščite približek faktorja 2 tako, da "
"izračunamo ujemanje v danem grafu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Our goal is to visualize the relationship of the matching and the minimum "
"vertex cover. For this, we want to specify two edge types, one to display "
"matching edges and one type to display <quote>ordinary</quote> edges, as "
"well as two node types that we use to distinguish nodes contained in C and "
"those not contained in C."
msgstr ""
"Naš cilj je vizualizirati razmerje ujemanja in minimalne pokritosti vozlišč. "
"Za to želimo določiti dva tipa robov, enega za prikaz ujemajočih se robov in "
"enega za prikaz <quote>navadnih</quote> robov, kot tudi dva tipa vozlišč, ki "
"ju uporabljamo za razlikovanje vozlišč, ki jih vsebuje C, in tistih, ki jih "
"C ne vsebuje ."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generating the Graph"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje grafa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For creating the graph, we use a default graph generator provided by &rocs;. "
"This can be found in the main menu at <menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Generate Graph</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. There, we select a <guilabel>Random Graph</"
"guilabel> with 30 nodes, 90 edges, and with seed 1 (the seed is the starting "
"seed for the random graph generator; using the same seed multiple times "
"results in same and reproducible graphs)."
msgstr ""
"Za izdelavo grafa uporabljamo privzeti generator grafov, ki ga ponuja "
"&rocs;. To lahko najdete v glavnem meniju v <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument "
"grafa</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Orodja</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ustvari graf</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Tam izberemo <guilabel>Naključni graf</guilabel> "
"s 30 vozlišči, 90 robovi in s semenom 1 (seme je začetno seme za generator "
"naključnih grafov; večkratna uporaba istega semena povzroči enake in "
"ponovljive grafe)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating the Element Types"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje vrst elementov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We use the <guilabel>Element Types</guilabel> and create a second node type "
"as well as a second edge type. For both new types we open the properties "
"dialog by using the respective <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Properties</guibutton> buttons and set the IDs "
"to <literal>2</literal>. Furthermore, we change the colors of elements of "
"these two new types (to distinguish them from the default types). Finally, "
"we set all edge types to be bidirectional, and the IDs of the default types "
"to <literal>1</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljamo <guilabel>Vrste elementov</guilabel> in ustvarimo drugo vrsto "
"vozlišča ter drugo vrsto roba. Za obe novi vrsti odpremo pogovorno okno z "
"lastnostmi z ustreznim <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-properties.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Lastnosti</guibutton> in nastavite ID-je na "
"<literal>2</literal>. Poleg tega spreminjamo barve elementov teh dveh novih "
"tipov (da jih razlikujemo od privzetih tipov). Končno smo vse tipe robov "
"nastavili na dvosmerne in ID-je privzetih tipov na <literal>1</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Algorithm"
msgstr "Algoritem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At last we have to implement the approximation algorithm. For this we use "
"the following implementation:"
msgstr ""
"Končno moramo implementirati aproksimacijski algoritem. Za to uporabljamo "
"naslednjo izvedbo:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"for (var i=0; i &lt; Document.nodes.length; i++) {\n"
"    Document.nodes[i].type = 1;\n"
"}\n"
"for (var i=0; i &lt; Document.edges.length; i++) {\n"
"    Document.edges[i].type = 1;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"var E = Document.edges(); // set of unprocessed edges\n"
"var C = new Array();      // matching edges\n"
"while (E.length > 0) {\n"
"    var e = E[0];         // we take first edge e={u,v}\n"
"    var u = e.from();\n"
"    var v = e.to();\n"
"    e.type = 2;           // set edge to be a matching edge\n"
"    E.shift();            // remove e (i.e., E[0]) from edge list\n"
"    C.push(u);            // add u to C\n"
"    C.push(v);            // add v to C\n"
"\n"
"    // mark u,v as nodes in C\n"
"    u.type = 2;\n"
"    v.type = 2;\n"
"\n"
"    // remove from E all edges incident to u or v\n"
"    var adjacent = u.edges();\n"
"    for (var i=0; i &lt; adjacent.length; i++) {\n"
"        var index = E.indexOf(adjacent[i]); // find the index\n"
"        if (index != -1) {\n"
"            E.splice(index, 1); // remove it if really found\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"    var adjacent = v.edges();\n"
"    for (var i=0; i &lt; adjacent.length; i++) {\n"
"        var index = E.indexOf(adjacent[i]); // find the index\n"
"        if (index != -1) {\n"
"            E.splice(index, 1); // remove it if really found\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"Console.log(\"Vertex Cover contains \" + C.length + \" nodes.\");"
msgstr ""
"for (var i=0; i &lt; Document.nodes.length; i++) {\n"
"    Document.nodes[i].type = 1;\n"
"}\n"
"for (var i=0; i &lt; Document.edges.length; i++) {\n"
"    Document.edges[i].type = 1;\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"var E = Document.edges(); // set of unprocessed edges\n"
"var C = new Array();      // matching edges\n"
"while (E.length > 0) {\n"
"    var e = E[0];         // we take first edge e={u,v}\n"
"    var u = e.from();\n"
"    var v = e.to();\n"
"    e.type = 2;           // set edge to be a matching edge\n"
"    E.shift();            // remove e (i.e., E[0]) from edge list\n"
"    C.push(u);            // add u to C\n"
"    C.push(v);            // add v to C\n"
"\n"
"    // mark u,v as nodes in C\n"
"    u.type = 2;\n"
"    v.type = 2;\n"
"\n"
"    // remove from E all edges incident to u or v\n"
"    var adjacent = u.edges();\n"
"    for (var i=0; i &lt; adjacent.length; i++) {\n"
"        var index = E.indexOf(adjacent[i]); // find the index\n"
"        if (index != -1) {\n"
"            E.splice(index, 1); // remove it if really found\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"    var adjacent = v.edges();\n"
"    for (var i=0; i &lt; adjacent.length; i++) {\n"
"        var index = E.indexOf(adjacent[i]); // find the index\n"
"        if (index != -1) {\n"
"            E.splice(index, 1); // remove it if really found\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}\n"
"Console.log(\"Vertex Cover contains \" + C.length + \" nodes.\");"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute the Algorithm"
msgstr "Izvedi algoritem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The algorithm can be executed by the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-start.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Run</"
"guibutton> button at the script control panel."
msgstr ""
"Algoritem lahko izvedete z gumbom <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"media-playback-start.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Zaženi</guibutton> na nadzorni plošči skripta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &rocs; User Interface"
msgstr "&rocs; Uporabniški vmesnik"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Elements of the User Interface"
msgstr "Glavni elementi uporabniškega vmesnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The user interface is divided into several logical parts as presented at the "
"screenshot below."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniški vmesnik je razdeljen na več logičnih delov, kot je prikazano na "
"spodnjem posnetku zaslona."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&GUI; elements of the &rocs; interface.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&GUI; elementi &rocs; vmesnik.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&GUI; elements of the &rocs; interface.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&GUI; elementi &rocs; vmesnik.</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graph Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik grafov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The editor provides a whiteboard at that nodes and edges can be placed. "
"Double-clicking at any of its elements opens a corresponding property menu. "
"You can use the tools from the <emphasis>Side Bar Tabs</emphasis> to create "
"and modify graphs."
msgstr ""
"Urejevalnik ponuja tablo, na katero je mogoče postaviti vozlišča in robove. "
"Z dvojnim klikom katerega koli od njegovih elementov se odpre ustrezen meni "
"lastnosti. Za ustvarjanje in spreminjanje grafov lahko uporabite orodja iz "
"<emphasis>zavihkov stranske vrstice</emphasis>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Available tools:"
msgstr "Razpoložljiva orodja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Top left in the box, your found the following action icons. Clicking at an "
"action means that your mouse pointer applies this action at the graph editor "
"whiteboard:"
msgstr ""
"Zgoraj levo v polju ste našli naslednje ikone dejanj. Klik na dejanje "
"pomeni, da kazalec miške uporabi to dejanje na tabli urejevalnika grafov:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Select and Move</guiicon>: To select elements, either click at "
"unused space at the whiteboard, keep the mouse pressed and draw a rectangle "
"that contains some data elements and/or edges to select these elements or "
"otherwise directly click at an unselected element to select this element. If "
"you click at a selected element or a set of selected elements, respectively, "
"by keeping the mouse pressed and moving around you can move these elements. "
"Moving selected elements is also possible with the arrow keys."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Izberi in premakni</guiicon>: Če želite izbrati elemente, bodisi "
"kliknite na neuporabljen prostor na tabli, držite miško pritisnjeno in "
"narišite pravokotnik, ki vsebuje nekaj podatkovnih elementov in/ali robov, "
"da izberete te elemente, ali kako drugače neposredno kliknite na neizbrani "
"element, da izberete ta element. Če kliknete na izbrani element ali niz "
"izbranih elementov, lahko te elemente premikate tako, da držite miško "
"pritisnjeno in se premikate. Premikanje izbranih elementov je možno tudi s "
"smernimi tipkami."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Add a Node</guiicon>: Click at an arbitrary position at the graph "
"editor whiteboard to create a new data element that belongs to the currently "
"selected data structure. By keeping the mouse pointer pressed at the button, "
"a menu shows up at which the data type of the new created data elements can "
"be selected (only if different data types exist)."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Dodaj vozlišče</guiicon>: Kliknite na poljuben položaj na tabli "
"urejevalnika grafov, da ustvarite nov podatkovni element, ki pripada "
"trenutno izbrani podatkovni strukturi. Če miškin kazalec držite pritisnjen "
"na gumbu, se prikaže meni, v katerem lahko izberete podatkovni tip novo "
"ustvarjenih podatkovnih elementov (le če obstajajo različni podatkovni tipi)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Create an Edge</guiicon>: Click at one data element, keep the mouse "
"pressed and draw a line to another data element to which the edge shall "
"point. This action is only successful if the current graph allows to add "
"this edge (&eg;, in an undirected graph you are not allowed to add multiple "
"edges between two data elements). By keeping the mouse pointer pressed at "
"the button, a menu shows up at which the edge type of the new created edges "
"can be selected (only if different edge types exist)."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Ustvari rob</guiicon>: kliknite na en podatkovni element, držite "
"miško pritisnjeno in narišite črto do drugega podatkovnega elementa, na "
"katerega bo kazal rob. To dejanje je uspešno samo, če trenutni graf omogoča "
"dodajanje tega roba (&eg;. v neusmerjenem grafu vam ni dovoljeno dodati več "
"robov med dva podatkovna elementa). Če miškin kazalec držite pritisnjen na "
"gumbu, se prikaže meni, v katerem lahko izberete vrsto robov novo "
"ustvarjenih robov (samo če obstajajo različni tipi robov)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon>Delete element</guiicon>: Click at an element to delete it. If you "
"delete a node, all adjacent edges are also deleted."
msgstr ""
"<guiicon>Izbriši element</guiicon>: Kliknite na element, da ga izbrišete. Če "
"izbrišete vozlišče, se izbrišejo tudi vsi sosednji robovi."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid "Side Bar"
msgstr "Stranska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the right, you can find the side bar that provides several tools for your "
"workflow:"
msgstr ""
"Na desni strani najdete stransko vrstico, ki ponuja več orodij za vaš potek "
"dela:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Element Types</guilabel>: This widget gives you direct access to "
"the available edge and node types."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vrste elementov</guilabel>: ta gradnik vam omogoča neposreden "
"dostop do razpoložljivih vrst robov in vozlišč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Journal</guilabel>: Each project has its own journal that can be "
"used to, &eg; note tasks, results, or observations."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dnevnik</guilabel>: Vsak projekt ima svoj dnevnik, ki ga lahko "
"uporabite za, &eg;. beleženje nalog, rezultatov ali opažanj."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Scripting API</guilabel>: To get direct access to the script "
"documentation, you can open this widget."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>API za skripte</guilabel>: Za neposreden dostop do dokumentacije "
"skripta lahko odprete ta gradnik."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik skript"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this text editor you can write algorithms as explained in detail in <xref "
"linkend=\"scripting\"/>. You can work on several script documents "
"simultaneously by using several tabs."
msgstr ""
"V tem urejevalniku besedil lahko pišete algoritme, kot je podrobno razloženo "
"v <xref linkend=\"scripting\"/>. Z uporabo več zavihkov lahko delate na več "
"dokumentih skripta hkrati."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script output:"
msgstr "Izhod skripta:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This text area either shows debug information or the script output of your "
"algorithm, depending on the toggled setting at the top of this widget. If "
"the script throws an error, automatically the debug output is presented."
msgstr ""
"To besedilno območje prikazuje informacije o odpravljanju napak ali rezultat "
"skripta vašega algoritma, odvisno od preklopne nastavitve na vrhu tega "
"pripomočka. Če skript vrže napako, se samodejno prikaže rezultat za "
"odpravljanje napak."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid "Controls"
msgstr "Kontrole"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can find the controls for executing scripts. You can execute the "
"script that is currently open at the script editor by pressing the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-start.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Run</"
"guibutton> button. While the script is executed, it is possible to stop "
"execution by pressing the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"process-stop.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Stop</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko najdete kontrolnike za izvajanje skriptov. Skript, ki je "
"trenutno odprt v urejevalniku skriptov, lahko izvedete tako, da pritisnete "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"media-playback-start.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Gumb<guibutton>Zaženi</"
"guibutton>. Medtem ko se skript izvaja, je mogoče ustaviti izvajanje s "
"pritiskom na gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"process-stop.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject><guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting"
msgstr "Skriptiranje"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:257
#, no-c-format
msgid "Executing Algorithms in &rocs;"
msgstr "Izvajanje algoritmov v &rocs;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; internally uses the QtScript &javascript; engine. This means, all "
"algorithms that you implement must use &javascript;. In the following, we "
"explain how to access and change elements of a graph document from the "
"scripting engine. It is important to note that changes done by the scripting "
"engine are directly reflected at the properties at the graph editor elements."
msgstr ""
"&rocs; interno uporablja motor QtScript &javascript;. To pomeni, da morajo "
"vsi algoritmi, ki jih izvajate, uporabljati &javascript;. V nadaljevanju "
"pojasnjujemo, kako dostopati in spreminjati elemente dokumenta grafa iz "
"skriptnega mehanizma. Pomembno je omeniti, da se spremembe, ki jih izvede "
"skriptni mehanizem, neposredno odražajo v lastnostih elementov urejevalnika "
"grafov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid "Control Script Execution"
msgstr "Izvajanje nadzornega skripta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are different execution modes for your algorithms:"
msgstr "Za vaše algoritme obstajajo različni načini izvajanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Run</guibutton>: Execute the script until it finishes."
msgstr "<guibutton>Zaženi</guibutton>: Izvaja skript, dokler se ne konča."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Stop</guibutton>: Stop script execution (only available while a "
"script is executed)."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Ustavi</guibutton>: Ustavi izvajanje skripta (na voljo samo med "
"izvajanjem skripta)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Output"
msgstr "Izhod skripta"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"During the execution of an algorithm, debug and program output is displayed "
"in the <emphasis>Debug &amp; Script Output</emphasis>. If the scripting "
"engine detects a syntax error in your script, the error is also displayed as "
"debug message. Note that all program messages are also displayed at the "
"debug output (displayed as bold text)."
msgstr ""
"Med izvajanjem algoritma je rezultat odpravljanja napak in programa prikazan "
"v <emphasis>Debug &amp; Izhod skripta</emphasis>. Če skriptni mehanizem "
"zazna sintaktično napako v vašem skriptu, se napaka prikaže tudi kot "
"sporočilo za odpravljanje napak. Upoštevajte, da so vsa sporočila programa "
"prikazana tudi na izhodu za odpravljanje napak (prikazano kot krepko "
"besedilo)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can control the text that is displayed at the script output by the "
"following functions:"
msgstr ""
"Besedilo, ki je prikazano na izhodu skripta, lahko nadzorujete z naslednjimi "
"funkcijami:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Console.log(string message);            // displays the message as script "
"output\n"
"    Console.debug(string message);          // displays the message as debug "
"output\n"
"    Console.error(string message);          // displays the message as error "
"output"
msgstr ""
"Console.log(string message);            // displays the message as script "
"output\n"
"    Console.debug(string message);          // displays the message as debug "
"output\n"
"    Console.error(string message);          // displays the message as error "
"output"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scripting Engine API"
msgstr "API skriptnega mehanizma"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The different parts of &rocs; each provide a static element that can be "
"accessed by the scripting engine. These are: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><userinput><command>Document</command></userinput> for the "
"graph document</para></listitem> "
"<listitem><para><userinput><command>Console</command></userinput> for the "
"console log output</para></listitem> </itemizedlist> For the explicit API "
"use and for a method reference, please see the inline help at the &rocs; "
"side bar."
msgstr ""
"Različni deli &rocs; vsak zagotavlja statični element, do katerega lahko "
"dostopa skriptni mehanizem. To so: <itemizedlist> "
"<listitem><para><userinput><command>Dokument</command></userinput> za "
"dokument z grafom</para></listitem> <listitem><para><userinput><command "
">Konzola</command></userinput> za izpis dnevnika konzole</para></listitem> </"
"itemizedlist> Za eksplicitno uporabo API-ja in referenco metode si oglejte "
"vgrajeno pomoč na &rocs; stranska vrstica."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export"
msgstr "Uvoz in izvoz"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:315
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exchange &rocs; Projects"
msgstr "Menjava &rocs; Projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; projects can be imported and exported as archived <literal role="
"\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal> files. These archives can be used to "
"exchange projects. Import and Export can be done with the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Graph...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> and <menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Export Graph As...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu items, "
"respectively."
msgstr ""
"&rocs; projekte je mogoče uvoziti in izvoziti kot arhivirane datoteke "
"<literal role=\"extension\">.tar.gz</literal>. Ti arhivi se lahko "
"uporabljajo za izmenjavo projektov. Uvoz in izvoz lahko izvedete z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Graph...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> in <menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi graf kot...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> elemente menija."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export of Graph Documents"
msgstr "Uvoz in izvoz grafičnih dokumentov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; currently supports import and export of the following file formats:"
msgstr "&rocs; trenutno podpira uvoz in izvoz naslednjih formatov datotek:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DOT; files, also known as Graphviz files"
msgstr "&DOT; datoteke, znane tudi kot datoteke Graphviz"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "<acronym>GML</acronym> files"
msgstr "datoteke <acronym>GML</acronym>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trivial Graph Format files"
msgstr "Datoteke Trivial Graph Format"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyhole Markup Language Format"
msgstr "Format označevalnega jezika Keyhole"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "Trivial Graph File Format"
msgstr "Format datoteke Trivial Graph"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis>Trivial Graph Format</emphasis> (<acronym>TGF</acronym>) is a "
"simple text-based file format for describing graphs. A <acronym>TGF</"
"acronym> file consists of a list of node definitions, that map the node IDs "
"to labels, followed by a list of the edges. In this format it is only "
"possible to have one label per node and one value per edge. &rocs; "
"interprets imported graphs as undirected graphs. Exported graphs will "
"contain two edges per connection if connections are bidirectional."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Trivialni grafični format</emphasis> (<acronym>TGF</acronym>) je "
"preprost besedilni format datoteke za opisovanje grafov. Datoteka "
"<acronym>TGF</acronym> je sestavljena iz seznama definicij vozlišč, ki "
"preslikajo ID-je vozlišč v oznake, ki jim sledi seznam robov. V tem formatu "
"je mogoče imeti samo eno oznako na vozlišče in eno vrednost na rob. &rocs; "
"interpretira uvožene grafe kot neusmerjene grafe. Če so povezave dvosmerne, "
"bodo izvoženi grafi vsebovali dva robova na povezavo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid "Format Specification"
msgstr "Specifikacija formata"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file starts with a list of nodes (one node per line), followed by a line "
"with the only character <quote>#</quote>, followed by a list of edges (one "
"edge per line)."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka se začne s seznamom vozlišč (eno vozlišče na vrstico), ki mu sledi "
"vrstica z edinim znakom <quote>#</quote>, ki ji sledi seznam robov (en rob "
"na vrstico)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A node consists of an integer (identifier), followed by a space, followed by "
"an arbitrary string."
msgstr ""
"Vozlišče je sestavljeno iz celega števila (identifikatorja), ki mu sledi "
"presledek, nato pa poljuben niz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An edge consists of two integers (identifiers) separated by a space, "
"followed by a space, followed by an arbitrary string. It is assumed that the "
"directed edge points from the first identifier to the second identifier."
msgstr ""
"Rob je sestavljen iz dveh celih števil (identifikatorjev), ločenih s "
"presledkom, ki mu sledi presledek in poljuben niz. Predpostavlja se, da "
"usmerjeni rob kaže od prvega identifikatorja do drugega identifikatorja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:351 index.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primer"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:352
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"1 starting node\n"
"2 transmitter\n"
"3 sink\n"
"#\n"
"1 2 blue\n"
"2 1 red\n"
"2 3 green"
msgstr ""
"1 starting node\n"
"2 transmitter\n"
"3 sink\n"
"#\n"
"1 2 blue\n"
"2 1 red\n"
"2 3 green"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DOT; Language / Graphviz Graph File Format"
msgstr "&DOT; Jezik / Oblika datoteke Graphviz Graph"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &DOT; language is a plain text graph description language that allows "
"both,a good human readable representation of graphs as well as an efficient "
"processing by graph layout programs. &DOT; is the default file format for "
"the Graphviz graph visualization suite, but is also widely used by other "
"graph tools. The usual file extensions for &DOT; are <literal role="
"\"extension\">.gv</literal> and <literal role=\"extension\">.dot</literal>."
msgstr ""
"&DOT; jezik je opisni jezik grafov z navadnim besedilom, ki omogoča tako "
"dobro človeku berljivo predstavitev grafov kot tudi učinkovito obdelavo s "
"programi za postavitev grafov. &DOT; je privzeti format datoteke za zbirko "
"za vizualizacijo grafov Graphviz, vendar ga pogosto uporabljajo tudi druga "
"orodja za grafe. Običajne končnice datotek za &DOT; sta <literal role="
"\"extension\">.gv</literal> in <literal role=\"extension\">.dot</literal>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Unsupported Features"
msgstr "Nepodprte funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; can parse every graph file that contains a graph specified according "
"to the &DOT; language specification<footnote><para>https://graphviz.org/doc/"
"info/lang.html</para></footnote>. The support of language features is "
"complete, despite of the following exceptions:"
msgstr ""
"&rocs; lahko razčleni vsako datoteko z grafom, ki vsebuje graf, določen "
"glede na &DOT; jezikovna specifikacija<footnote><para>https://graphviz.org/"
"doc/info/lang.html</para></footnote>. Podpora za jezikovne funkcije je "
"popolna, kljub naslednjim izjemam:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"subgraph: Due to the lack of a subgraph concept in &rocs;, subgraphs are "
"only imported as a set of date elements and connections. Especially, "
"connections to or from subgraphs are not imported."
msgstr ""
"podgraf: Zaradi pomanjkanja koncepta podgrafa v &rocs; so podgrafi uvoženi "
"le kot nabor datumskih elementov in povezav. Zlasti povezave do ali iz "
"podgrafov niso uvožene."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&HTML; and &XML; attributes: Attributes (like labels) that contain &HTML; or "
"&XML; syntax are read unchanged. Especially, not adjustment of fonts and "
"styles are read from those attributes."
msgstr ""
"&HTML; in &XML; atributi: atributi (kot so oznake), ki vsebujejo &HTML; ali "
"&XML; sintaksa se bere nespremenjena. Še posebej, prilagoditve pisav in "
"slogov se ne berejo iz teh atributov."

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"digraph myGraph {\n"
"    a -> b -> c;\n"
"    b -> d;\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"digraph myGraph {\n"
"    a -> b -> c;\n"
"    b -> d;\n"
"}"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "Graph Layout"
msgstr "Postavitev grafa"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid "Laying out graphs automatically in &rocs;"
msgstr "Samodejno postavitev grafov v &rocs;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rocs; can lay out graphs automatically. The &rocs; graph layout tool can be "
"found in the main menu at <menuchoice><guimenu>Graph Document</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Tools</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Graph Layout</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. There are two different layout algorithms that can be applied: "
"Force Based Layout and Radial Tree Layout. To apply one of them, select the "
"corresponding tab of the graph layout tool, choose the desired parameters "
"and execute the algorithm by pressing on the <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"button. Details that are specific to each one of the layout algorithms are "
"provided in the next sections."
msgstr ""
"&rocs; lahko samodejno postavi grafe. &rocs; orodje za postavitev grafa "
"najdete v glavnem meniju v <menuchoice><guimenu>Dokument grafa</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Orodja</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Postavitev grafa</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Uporabiti je mogoče dva različna algoritma postavitve: Force "
"Based Layout in Radial Tree Layout. Če želite uporabiti enega od njih, "
"izberite ustrezen zavihek orodja za postavitev grafa, izberite želene "
"parametre in zaženite algoritem s pritiskom na gumb <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton>. Podrobnosti, ki so specifične za vsakega od algoritmov "
"postavitve, so navedene v naslednjih razdelkih."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force Based Layout"
msgstr "Force Based Layout"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Force Based Layout can be applied to any graph. Intuitively, this "
"algorithm simulates forces acting in each node. There are repelling forces "
"between pairs of nodes and attraction forces between pairs of nodes that are "
"neighbours. The magnitude of these forces can be specified by moving the "
"corresponding sliders in the user interface."
msgstr ""
"Force Based Layout je mogoče uporabiti za kateri koli graf. Intuitivno ta "
"algoritem simulira sile, ki delujejo v vsakem vozlišču. Med pari vozlišč "
"delujejo odbojne sile, med pari vozlišč, ki so soseda, pa privlačne sile. "
"Velikost teh sil je mogoče določiti s premikanjem ustreznih drsnikov v "
"uporabniškem vmesniku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:403
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A Screenshot of the Force Based Layout tab of the &rocs; graph "
"layout tool.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona zavihka Force Based Layout aplikacije &rocs; "
"orodje za postavitev grafa.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A Screenshot of the Force Based Layout tab of the &rocs; graph "
"layout tool.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona zavihka Force Based Layout v aplikaciji &rocs; "
"orodje za postavitev grafa.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another parameter that can be controlled is the Area Factor. This parameter "
"controls how the nodes are spread. Layouts generated with high values of "
"Area Factor have a tendency of having large distances between nodes."
msgstr ""
"Drugi parameter, ki ga je mogoče nadzorovati, je faktor površine. Ta "
"parameter nadzoruje, kako so vozlišča razporejena. Postavitve, ustvarjene z "
"visokimi vrednostmi faktorja površine, imajo običajno velike razdalje med "
"vozlišči."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Radial Tree Layout"
msgstr "Radialna postavitev drevesa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Radial Tree Layout can only be applied to trees. Any attempt to apply "
"this layout algorithm to other kinds of graph will produce an error message. "
"Parameters for the Radial Tree Layout can be selected using the provided "
"user interface."
msgstr ""
"Radialno drevesno postavitev je mogoče uporabiti samo za drevesa. Vsak "
"poskus uporabe tega algoritma postavitve za druge vrste grafov bo povzročil "
"sporočilo o napaki. Parametre za postavitev radialnega drevesa je mogoče "
"izbrati s priloženim uporabniškim vmesnikom."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A Screenshot of the Radial Tree Layout tab of the &rocs; graph "
"layout tool.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona zavihka Radialna drevesna postavitev aplikacije "
"&rocs; orodje za postavitev grafa.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A Screenshot of the Radial Tree Layout tab of the &rocs; graph "
"layout tool.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona zavihka Radialna drevesna postavitev v aplikaciji "
"&rocs; orodje za postavitev grafa.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tree type parameter selects between a free tree layout and a rooted tree "
"layout. In a free tree layout, nodes are placed freely without any apparent "
"hierarchy between them. In a rooted tree layout, the root node is placed at "
"the top and sub-trees are laid out below it, giving an idea of a hierarchy "
"between nodes."
msgstr ""
"Parameter drevesne vrste izbira med prosto drevesno postavitvijo in "
"ukoreninjeno drevesno postavitvijo. V prosti drevesni postavitvi so vozlišča "
"prosto postavljena brez kakršne koli očitne hierarhije med njimi. Pri "
"zakoreninjeni drevesni postavitvi je korensko vozlišče postavljeno na vrh, "
"poddrevesa pa so postavljena pod njim, kar daje predstavo o hierarhiji med "
"vozlišči."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The center/root parameter defines which node is going be used as root for "
"the rooted tree layout or as center for the free tree layout. The center of "
"a free tree layout is the first node to be placed by the algorithm. All "
"other nodes are placed on circles centered at the center node. A center/root "
"can be selected automatically by the layout algorithm."
msgstr ""
"Parameter center/root določa, katero vozlišče bo uporabljeno kot korensko za "
"postavitev ukoreninjenega drevesa ali kot središče za postavitev prosta "
"drevesa. Središče proste drevesne postavitve je prvo vozlišče, ki ga postavi "
"algoritem. Vsa druga vozlišča so postavljena na kroge s središčem v "
"osrednjem vozlišču. Središče/koren lahko samodejno izbere algoritem "
"postavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The node separation parameter controls the distance between nodes. "
"Increasing the value of this parameter will cause the distance between nodes "
"to increase. Similarly, decreasing the value of this parameter will cause "
"the distance between nodes to decrease."
msgstr ""
"Parameter ločevanja vozlišč nadzira razdaljo med vozlišči. Povečanje "
"vrednosti tega parametra bo povzročilo povečanje razdalje med vozlišči. "
"Podobno bo zmanjšanje vrednosti tega parametra povzročilo zmanjšanje "
"razdalje med vozlišči."

